description: Right about now, you’ll want some Funk Seoul Brother, for the best Sushi Burritos and Korean Street Food that you’ll ever nosh on in Nashville.This amazing team fuses the best of Korean and Japanese cuisine in order to offer a reimagined twist on a few of our favorite authentic dishes; Korean BBQ Tacos with Bulgogi Beef, Gochujang BBQ Sauce, Shaved Cabbage, Sriracha Aioli, and Ginger Scallion Salsa, Crunchy Tempura Shrimp Burrito with Shaved Cabbage, Cucumber, Carrot, Avocado, Tempura Flakes, Sriracha May, and Gari Ginger-these are only a couple of their incredible creations, so step right up to this funkadelic truck and fuel your soul with all the lovely food from Funk Seoul Brother.
name: Funk Seoul Brother
